# Assets directory for future images and media files
# 
# Usage:
#   - Place images, videos, and media files in this directory
#   - Reference them in HTML: <img src="public/assets/image.png" alt="...">
#   - This directory is tracked by git to preserve structure
#
# Example structure:
#   public/assets/images/
#   public/assets/videos/
#   public/assets/icons/
#   public/assets/fonts/
